text: Sharon Chepchumba Kiprono (born 26 October 1998) is a Kenyan volleyball player. She is part of the Kenya women's national volleyball team. She participated in the 2018 FIVB Volleyball World Grand Prix. She won a gold medal at the 2019 African Games. At the club level, she plays for KCB. == References == Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Kenyan volleyball players
